<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/52602ANBHGMCCSGJPHTBMJQTSTLJMSQNV> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Bageshree Vaze and Vineet Vyas: In the Darbar";
  schema:description """
	Experience Indo-Canadian artist Bageshree Vaze, an acclaimed Kathak and Bharatanatyam dancer, vocalist, and 2022 Dora Award–winning composer, alongside tabla artist Vineet Vyas. <span class=\"ItalicText\">In the Darbar</span> brings North Indian classical dance and music to life through a dynamic exchange between dancer and drummer, celebrating Indo-Canadian identity with dazzling spins, intricate footwork, and rich rhythm.
""";
