<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/55401ACNDTGGQPPPTRVGVMSDRVVBMKVVG> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Canadian League of Composers 75th Anniversary: Past Presidents’ Piano Recital with John Burge";
  schema:description """
	Canadian League of Composers 75th Anniversary: Past Presidents’ Piano Recital celebrates 75 years of Canadian creativity with a solo program curated and performed by composer and pianist John Burge. Featuring works by many of the CLC’s Past Presidents, the recital opens with Beverley McKiver’s <span class=\"ItalicText\">Trillium</span> and concludes with a stirring rendition of <span class=\"ItalicText\">O Canada</span>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This 75-minute tribute honours the legacy and leadership of the Canadian League of Composers through music and reflection.
""";
