<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/56002ACDVJDVLHKLRBQGBCGKBSNGJCGLL> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Delirium Musicum";
  schema:description """
	Founded in 2018, Delirium Musicum is a dynamic Los Angeles-based ensemble known for virtuosic energy, inventive programming, and a vibrant, boundary-crossing approach to music. The program includes <span class=\"ItalicText\">Recomposed by Max Richter: Vivaldi – The Four Seasons</span>, alongside a selection of short, diverse pieces from the ensemble’s second Warner Classics album, <span class=\"ItalicText\">Cabinet of Curiosities</span>.
""";
