<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/53001ACMLBMKGCRKLTKVJLVJTHVVQTDSS> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Harvest Moon Celebration with David R. Maracle";
  schema:description """
	David R. Maracle, Bear Clan<span><br/></span>Tehanenia’kwè:tarons<span><br/></span>Cutter of Stone<span><br/></span>Mohawks of the Bay of Quinte<span><br/></span>Kenhtè:ke Kanyen’kehá:ka<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Award-winning Haudenosaunee artist David R. Maracle is a multi-instrumentalist, composer, and producer whose work blends ancestral teachings with modern creativity. Since 1985, he has created exceptional stone sculptures and music, earning multiple Canadian Indigenous Music Awards, two RIAA Gold Records, and international performances including the 2000 Olympics and for the Queen of England.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This performance is a celebration of harvest, gratitude, and the enduring traditions of Indigenous Peoples.
""";
