  schema:name "Jupiter Ensemble";
  schema:description """
	The Jupiter Ensemble unites some of today’s most dynamic young period-instrument artists in performances of electrifying energy and artistry. Internationally acclaimed for their award-winning recordings and appearances at major venues worldwide, the ensemble brings fresh vitality to Baroque repertoire.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This program explores the myth of the Amazons in music by Antonio Vivaldi, Francesco Cavalli, André Cardinal Destouches, and others, weaving drama, brilliance, and instrumental colour into a thrilling musical journey.
