<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/49801AVVVJQRDHHCHGRNLMSSLHRNCVBPM> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Lightfoot Band";
  schema:description """
	The Lightfoot Band—not a tribute, but the original musicians who toured and recorded with Gordon Lightfoot now coming together to honour his legacy and keep his music alive. Featuring Rick Haynes, Barry Keane, Mike Heffernan, Carter Lancaster, and newest member, singer Andy Mauck, they perform beloved hits like Sundown, If You Could Read My Mind, and The Wreck of the Edmund Fitzgerald, plus rarely heard gems. Along with the music, they share behind-the-scenes stories from their years on the road. Come for the songs and hear the stories! A heartfelt celebration of a musical icon, brought to life by those who knew him best.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLW8fA0x1r8C9JUEcwN_LROrTlFcWq1Zgm\">Watch highlights from The Lightfoot Band here!</a>
""";
