  schema:name "VOCES8";
  schema:description """
	The internationally acclaimed British vocal ensemble VOCES8 comes to the Isabel this July, bringing their luminous sound and signature precision to a special co-presentation with Ottawa Chamberfest. Celebrated worldwide for their clarity, blend, and artistry, VOCES8 delivers performances that captivate audiences from the first note. Experience one of the world’s leading vocal ensembles in an evening of pure vocal brilliance.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This performance is co-presented by the Isabel Bader Centre for the Performing Arts and Ottawa Chamberfest.
""";
